OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775481061
OL,3,C40-year-old woman charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after man stabbed
OL,5,Cnear Lincoln
OL,7,FA woman has been charged with
OL,8,Fattempted murder after a man was found
OL,9,Fwith suspected stab wounds at a
OL,10,Fproperty near Lincoln.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to a property on
OL,13,FDixon Place just before 8pm on
OL,14,FWednesday 1 April, after receiving a
OL,15,Freport that a man was seriously
OL,16,Finjured from suspected stab wounds.
OL,18,FThe man was taken to hospital where he
OL,19,Fremans in critical condition.
