OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775481061
OL,3,C40-year-old woman charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after man stabbed
OL,5,Cnear Lincoln
OL,7,FMia Mcilwee, aged 40, of Dixon Place,
OL,8,FDunholme was charged with attempted
OL,9,Fmurder on Thursday 2 April.
OL,11,FShe is remanded to custody ahead of
OL,12,Fher next appearance at Lincoln
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday 4 April.
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police are appealing for
OL,16,Fanyone with information to come
OL,17,Fforward.
